      <h1 class='title'>Millennium Dome</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1652WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1652ws' title='Col. 1652WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1652WS' name='column_1652ws' href='#column_1652ws' rel='bookmark'>1652WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_21'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/dr-bob-spink' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_21' title='Link to this speech by Dr Bob Spink' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/dr-bob-spink" title="Dr Bob Spink">Bob Spink</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Deputy Prime Minister if he will make a statement on the schedule of maintenance and repairs for the Millennium Dome. [189319]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_22'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-keith-hill' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_22' title='Link to this speech by Mr Keith Hill' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-keith-hill" title="Mr Keith Hill">Keith Hill</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">The dome has been maintained under the terms of the contracts with MDL and Anschutz in order to hand over the dome for the construction of the arena and surrounding waterfront development. It has also been maintained sufficiently to enable it to be hired for short-term events in order to mitigate running costs.</p><p>The planned preventative maintenance regime that has been adopted covers the following categories of maintenance: fabric and supporting steelwork; air management system; water and drainage systems; services and plant lighting; CCTV; voice alarm; fire alarm; landscaping; perimeter fence; and operational buildings required.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
